### ============== PUBLIC MENU ROUTES ==============

### 1. Get All Menus (Basic)
GET {{baseUrl}}/menus
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 2. Get All Menus with Pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/menus?page=1&limit=5
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 3. Filter by Vendor Category
GET {{baseUrl}}/menus?vendorCategory=home_chef
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 4. Filter by Cuisine
GET {{baseUrl}}/menus?cuisine=indian
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 5. Filter by Dietary Options
GET {{baseUrl}}/menus?dietaryOptions=vegetarian,vegan
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 6. Filter by Tags
GET {{baseUrl}}/menus?tags=healthy,organic
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 7. Filter by Availability
GET {{baseUrl}}/menus?isAvailable=true
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 8. Search Menus
GET {{baseUrl}}/menus?search=chicken curry
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 9. Sort by Price (Ascending)
GET {{baseUrl}}/menus?sortBy=price&sortOrder=asc
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 10. Sort by Rating (Descending)
GET {{baseUrl}}/menus?sortBy=rating.average&sortOrder=desc
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 11. Sort by Prep Time
GET {{baseUrl}}/menus?sortBy=prepTime&sortOrder=asc
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 12. Sort by Calories
GET {{baseUrl}}/menus?sortBy=calories&sortOrder=desc
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 13. Sort by Created Date
GET {{baseUrl}}/menus?sortBy=createdAt&sortOrder=desc
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 14. Complex Filter Example
GET {{baseUrl}}/menus?vendorCategory=home_chef&cuisine=indian&dietaryOptions=vegetarian&isAvailable=true&sortBy=rating.average&sortOrder=desc&page=1&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### 15. Get Menu by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/menus/{{menuId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{adminToken}}

### ============== ADMIN MENU ROUTES ==============

### 16. Create New Menu
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/menus
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "foodImage": "https://example.com/food-image.jpg",
  "foodSubImages": [
    "https://example.com/sub-image1.jpg",
    "https://example.com/sub-image2.jpg"
  ],
  "foodTitle": "Delicious Chicken Biryani Premium",
  "price": 299,
  "description": {
    "short": "Aromatic basmati rice cooked with tender chicken pieces and exotic spices",
    "long": "A traditional recipe passed down through generations, featuring premium basmati rice, succulent chicken pieces marinated in yogurt and spices, slow-cooked to perfection with saffron, caramelized onions, and fresh herbs."
  },
  "detailedItemList": "Basmati Rice, Chicken (500g), Yogurt, Onions, Ginger-Garlic Paste, Biryani Masala, Saffron, Mint Leaves, Coriander Leaves, Ghee",
  "vendorCategory": "home_chef",
  "cuisine": "Indian",
  "prepTime": 45,
  "calories": 650,
  "dietaryOptions": ["non-vegetarian", "dairy-free"],
  "tags": ["spicy", "traditional", "aromatic"]
}

### 17. Update Menu
PUT {{baseUrl}}/admin/menus/{{menuId}}
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 349,
  "description": {
    "short": "Premium Chicken Biryani with extra saffron and nuts"
  }
}

### 18. Delete Menu
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/admin/menus/{{menuId}}
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 19. Toggle Menu Availability
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/menus/{{menuId}}/toggle-availability
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 20. Update Menu Rating
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/menus/{{menuId}}/rating
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "rating": 4.5
}

### 21. Bulk Update Menu Availability
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/menus/bulk-availability
Authorization: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "menuIds": [
    "67892abcdef123456789abcd",
    "67892abcdef123456789abce",
